@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.74 - v0 + 0.92) + (v2 + 0.93 / v2 + 0.04)) / (v2 + tmp))
    v1 = (tmp - wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.29)))
    tmp = (tmp * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.35) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.70)))
    data[tid] = v0
